Can anyone find this Fuji brand shutter release cable? /!/ I want to buy [this](https://fujiuser.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Shuttercable-2.jpg) Fujifilm brand shutter release cable but I can't find it anywhere. I know it doesn't have to be that one and that there are plenty others that will work, but I want that one. I hope y'all can understand. I've scraped the internet for it and can only find it on some guys blog that's no longer active. I tried to reach out to the blog owner but I can't find any place he's still active online. So as my last resort I'm hoping that the fine folks of r/Fujifilm will know something.

Here's another [photo](https://fujiuser.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Shuttercable-3.jpg) if it helps.

Thanks for reading!
